{"article_id":"MGx3LDuCi3MH5ASz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A national school walk-out is planned next month by the organizers of the Women 's March","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to protest Congress ' lack of action on gun reform","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"following mass shootings ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The Hill reported Saturday .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Students , teachers and parents are invited to participate in the event","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"titled Women 's March Youth EMPOWER ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"which will be a 17-minute walkout on March 14 at 10 a.m .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The city of the country 's latest mass school shooting , Parkland , Florida , is one of the sites","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"where a walkout is planned .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Women 's March Youth EMPOWER is calling for students , teachers , and allies to take part in a # NationalSchoolWalkout for 17 minutes at 10am on March 14 , 2018 .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Join us","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"in saying # ENOUGH !","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"https : //t.co/8ZE8uthRlZ","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"pic.","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"twitter.com/45yCZl4zDm","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"-","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Women 's March","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"( @ womensmarch )","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"February 16 , 2018","depth":3},{"id":19,"text":"`` We need action .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"Students and allies are organizing the national school walkout","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"to demand Congress pass legislation","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to keep us safe from gun violence at our schools , on our streets and in our homes and places of worship , ''","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the group 's website said .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` Students and staff have the right","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to teach and learn in an environment","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"free from the worry","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"of being gunned down in their classrooms or on their way home from school .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"`` Parents have the right","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to send their kids to school in the mornings","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and see them home alive at the end of the day .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"`` We are not safe at school .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"We are not safe in our cities and towns .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"Congress must take meaningful action","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"to keep us safe","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and pass federal gun reform legislation","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"that address the public health crisis of gun violence .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Two dozen walkouts across the country are already planned ,","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"according to the organizers ' website ,","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"which also includes information for other localities","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"wishing to participate .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"The walkout event follows the deadly mass shooting on Wednesday at Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School in Florida","depth":4},{"id":42,"text":"which left 17 dead .","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"Nikolas Cruz , the 19-year-old suspect in the shooting , claimed","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"`` demon '' voices told him to carry out the violence ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"according to law enforcement sources .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":91,"left":64,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":61,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":54,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":49,"right":53,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":48,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":48,"left":47,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":47,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"elabor